author: Corridor Crew
description: The Amazing Bulk is easily one of the best worst movies ever made. A 2012 parody of The Amazing Hulk that quickly goes off the rails, filled with pure randomness and some of the most impressively terrible VFX you’ll ever see. It's so bad... that it kind of circles back to being good?
title: Is The Amazing Bulk more INCREDIBLE than The Hulk?
